  "text": "Group satisfaction. This variable was measured using a multi-item scale asking students to report their satisfaction with the group process, as well as the final output. Five-point scales were used for each of the items, with 1 indicating extremely dissatisfied and 5 extremely satisfied. The [CITATION_1] alpha for the multi-item scale was .92.",
